cassandra installation - Windows:
=================================
1. Download datastax community edition
2. bug with cdc_raw_directory:
error details:
2017-03-20 23:07:47 Commons Daemon procrun stderr initialized
cdc_raw_directory is missing and -Dcassandra.storagedir is not set

to resolve this issue set the cdc_raw_directory: C:\Program Files\DataStax-DDC\data\cdc_raw
link: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/40261374/datastax-ddc-service-will-not-start